/span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Java</span><span style="font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">类和对象的概念</span></p>\n  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span><span style="font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">类是对某一类事物的描述<span lang="EN-US">(</span>共性<span lang="EN-US">)</span>，是抽象的、概念上的定义；</span></p>\n  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span><span style="font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">对象则是实际存在的属该类事物的具体的个体（个性），因而也称为实例\n  <span lang="EN-US">(Instance) </span>。</span></p>\n  <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:36.0pt;text-indent:-36.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">（2）<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  </span></span><span style="font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">定义类</span></p>\n  <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:31.5pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">[</span><span style="font-family:\n  &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">类修饰符<span lang="EN-US">] class </span>类名称<span lang="EN-US">[extends\n  </span>父类名称<span lang="EN-US">]</span></span></p>\n  <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:31.5pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  {&nbsp; //</span><span style="font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">声明成员变量</span></p>\n  <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:31.5pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  [</span><span style="font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">修饰符<span lang="EN-US">] </spa